{"tid":1467050,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"概然不分割","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:49.000Z","uid":237712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf0a6285ada1583f6ae95ceb1ac1354366547db","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"概然不分割<br />\n概然大家係同一team人<br />\n點解任何行動前唔可以拎出嚟討論<br />\n如果討論完大部分同意咪去做<br />\n但而家大家意見一半一半嘅時候<br />\n點解係一味互屌然後各自硬做<br />\n而唔係傾個大家都同意嘅方法<br />\nE.g行動前一晚開個post正負評決定做唔做<br />\n（未必完美 拋磚引玉）"},{"pid":"6f11947880e47b5098b2c96a2133a8b0110806d5","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"833778b8de28b5acf6740a42cfd33dc2363f0d8c","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"c788ef4ae552cfb5b3d915a6b2a99860e22cf721","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"816見"},{"pid":"288a7af68aff955bf949e6e914c3b0cfb6ddf205","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"818見"},{"pid":"d67192c0d791934962fb5c273b2f0d6d68b8bb73","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a1cbac7c9d3947ce4634324c46a8500dc8cabc4","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c1880c2fdef0d41897ec8215e62d1fff52ecdb8e","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d559fe78d4a1869f21e94988bae2ff72f966a87e","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:48.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"44600eca15bec7cf9ae1f03bd654a6cf6f07bdb8","tid":1467050,"uid":237712,"like":0,